OL,3,CRobert Jenrick: Scrap the Sentencing
OL,4,CCouncil to prevent 'two-tier' justice
OL,6,F"Never again can the British people
OL,7,Fface the prospect of two-tier justice."
OL,9,FEarlier this year, concerns were
OL,10,Fraised after the council, responsible
OL,11,Ffor setting guidelines on sentencing,
OL,12,Fissued guidance recommending judges
OL,13,Ftake into account factors such as
OL,14,Fethnicity or gender when deciding
OL,15,Fwhether to ask for a pre-sentence
OL,16,Freport.
OL,18,FJenrick and others said the guidance
OL,19,Fwould result in people facing a lesser
OL,20,Fpunishment on the basis of their
OL,21,Fethnicity.
