OL,6,FThe proposal was withdrawn, and the
OL,7,Fgovernment has introduced legislation
OL,8,Fto require any new guidance to be
OL,9,Fapproved by ministers.
OL,11,FIn his speech on Tuesday, Jenrick is
OL,12,Fexpected to say: "We are slipping into
OL,13,Fa two-tier nightmare under Keir
OL,14,FStarmer.
OL,16,F"All too frequently, the law is not
OL,17,Fapplied equally.
OL,19,F"No more, every single person in this
OL,20,Fcountry must be treated exactly the
OL,21,Fsame, regardless of their background."
