OL,6,FA Labour Party spokesperson accused
OL,7,Fthe Conservatives of "yet more rank
OL,8,Fhypocrisy," adding: "The Conservatives
OL,9,Fbacked the proposed changes to pre-
OL,10,Fsentencing reports when they were
OL,11,Fannounced and did nothing to stop them
OL,12,Fwhen they were in government.
OL,14,F"Labour took action the moment we
OL,15,Funcovered their mistake.
OL,17,F"This is just another cynical gimmick
OL,18,Ffrom Jenrick, a man who constantly
OL,19,Fundermines the independence of the
OL,20,Fjudiciary just to further his own
OL,21,Fcareer."
