OL,6,F"My expectation is that Kemi will lead
OL,7,Fthis party into the next general
OL,8,Felection," Robert Jenrick told The
OL,9,FSpectator.
OL,11,FJenrick's speech comes on the third
OL,12,Fday of a conference in which the party
OL,13,Fhas been determined to demonstrate
OL,14,Funity despite its polling difficulties
OL,15,Fand questions about Kemi Badenoch's
OL,16,Fleadership.
OL,18,FThe former leadership contender, who
OL,19,Fhas recently taken up boxing, has been
OL,20,Finsistent that he is backing Badenoch.
